commit.message:
c-opts.c, [...]: Update copyright.

	* c-opts.c, expmed.c, gengtype.c, tree-complex.c,
	config/arm/iwmmxt.md, config/avr/avr.c, config/s390/s390.h:
	Update copyright.

From-SVN: r94154
